    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 it is best suited for buyers who are experienced with repairs, looking for a project car, or need a parts vehicle. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible rust, dents, and scratched or faded paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn and shows signs of heavy use, with damaged upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and will require attention before it can be considered fully road-ready; buyers should anticipate investing additional time and money into repairs. There are no representations made about emissions or safety inspection readiness. This listing is priced to reflect the true state of the vehicle, and we encourage interested buyers to inspect it thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
